list.abstract: late是一个英语单词，可以用作形容词和副词，可以翻译为晚的、迟到的，等等。
《Late》是英格兰流行唱作女歌手弗洛丽发行的第三张迷你专辑，专辑内部共收录4首歌曲，2012年5月31日通过唱片公司发行。

yingyinNormal.en: Excuse me. Sorry. I'm late.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不好意思，来晚了。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't be late home, Daddy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不要太晚回家哦，爸爸。

yingyinNormal.en: It's late. Got to go. Bye.
yingyinNormal.zh: 时间晚了，要睡了，再见。

yingyinNormal.en: You're too late. It's gone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你来得太晚了。都结束了。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll kiss your staff. Too late.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我亲吻权杖。太晚了。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb》

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, it's so late for "shall we."
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在说“好吗”时间有点太晚了。

yingyinNormal.en: Hi. Thanks for showing up 30 minutes late.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嗨，谢天谢地，你才晚了30分钟。

yingyinNormal.en: Guys, sorry I'm late. I have amazing news.
yingyinNormal.zh: 各位，抱歉来晚了，我有个好消息。

yingyinNormal.en: Sheldon, what are you doing here so late?
yingyinNormal.zh: Sheldon这么晚了你来这儿干嘛?

yingyinNormal.en: He's barely ticking. We fear you are too late.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他的心跳很微弱。只怕你来得太晚了。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《爱丽丝梦游仙境2：镜中奇遇记》

yingyinNormal.en: Here's your present, Peppa. Sorry it's a bit late.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是给你的礼物佩奇。 对不起有点晚了。

yingyinNormal.en: How early are we? Oh, actually, we're an hour late.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们早到很久吗？其实我们晚到了一个小时。

yingyinNormal.en: Dry-cleaning? If it's too much... If it's too late...
yingyinNormal.zh: 干洗？如果要求过分了点，又或者时间太晚...

yingyinNormal.en: What about your girlfriend? It's too late. I call dibs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那你的女朋友呢？太晚了，我说了这个归我了。

yingyinNormal.en: You're up late.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你起晚了。

yingyinNormal.en: Too late for that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说的太晚了。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey. Am I late? Am I late? Nobody came out yet, right?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我来晚了吗？还没有人出来吧？

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, hey, guys. Hey. Sorry we're late. Late? It's 7:05. And you said the party starts at 7:00.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嗨，各位，嘿，对不起，来晚了。晚？才7:05呢。你说过派对7点开始。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, is it too late out there? I know you're usually up late, right? No, I was just catching up on some paperwork. Good.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在给你打电话，是不是太晚了？我记得你经常熬夜？不晚，我刚刚在赶一批文件。太好了。

yingyinNormal.en: It's too late. No, it's not. Leave here with me. Come home. We miss you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 太晚了。不，并不晚，跟我离开这里，跟我回家，我们很想你。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: adj. 后半部分的；后者；第二个；最近的；最后阶段的

word_family.mean: adj. 晚的；迟的；迟来的；已故的；最近的；最新的；后期；以前的；原来的；晚期的

sense_info_list.en: of recent date

examination_example.sentence: The responsibility for the <highlight>latest</highlight> wave of strikes rests on the unions.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 最近罢工潮的责任在于工会。

examination_example.sentence: In its <highlight>latest</highlight> survey of CEO pay, The Wall Street Journal finds that "a substantial part" of executive pay is now tied to performance.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 《华尔街日报》对CEO薪酬的最新调查发现，高管薪酬中“很大一部分”现在与业绩挂钩。

examination_example.sentence: Younger Americans are drawing a new 21st-century road map to success, a <highlight>latest</highlight> poll has found.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一项最新民意调查发现，美国的年轻人正在寻找21世纪的成功之道。

sense_info_list.en: belonging or taking place near the end of a particular time or period

examination_example.sentence: The country produces only about 60 per cent of the food it eats, down from almost three-quarters in the <highlight>late</highlight> 1980s.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 该国的粮食产量仅占其所食用粮食的60%左右，低于上世纪80年代末的近四分之三。

examination_example.sentence: Sometimes I feel in his <highlight>late</highlight> works a will to break all signs of continuity.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有时我在他的晚期作品中感受到一种打破所有连续符号的欲望。

examination_example.sentence: In the <highlight>late</highlight> 1800s British archaeologist Sir Arthur Evans combed antique dealers' stores in Athens, Greece.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 19世纪末，英国考古学家亚瑟·埃文斯爵士仔细梳理了希腊雅典的古董商商店。

sense_info_list.en: doing something or taking place after the expected, proper, or usual time

examination_example.sentence: Have you noticed that you can leave on a flight an hour <highlight>late</highlight> but still arrive on time?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你有没有注意到你乘晚点一小时的飞机离开，也能准时到达?

examination_example.sentence: People complained that buses were <highlight>late</highlight> and infrequent.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 人们抱怨公共汽车迟到，车次又少。

examination_example.sentence: One survey found that bureaucratic delays led the average H-2A worker to arrive on the job 22 days <highlight>late</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一项调查发现，官僚主义的拖延导致H-2A员工平均上班迟到22天。

sense_info_list.en: (of a specified person) no longer alive; no longer having the specified status

examination_example.sentence: The <highlight>late</highlight> psychologist Nalini Ambady asked participants to watch silent 10-second video clips of professors.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 已故心理学家纳里尼·阿姆巴迪要求参与者观看有关教授的10秒无声视频片段。

sense_info_list.en: the most recent news or fashion

word_usage.usage: late和lately均为副词，但late与作形容词的late意义相似，而lately只含近来之意。

都指“后来”
later指正在谈论的过去某个时间点之后，常和具体时间段连用；也可指现在之后。
afterwards指在已提及的某事件或时间点之后，一般不和具体时间段连用。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: adj. 后半部分的；后者；第二个；最近的；最后阶段的

word_family.mean: adj. 晚的；迟的；迟来的；已故的；最近的；最新的；后期；以前的；原来的；晚期的

sense_info_list.en: at a time in the future

examination_example.sentence: But the first phase—a passion for invention—is not a reliable indicator that the firm will still be open for business a few years <highlight>later</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但是第一阶段——对发明的热情——并不是一个表明公司几年后还会持续营业的可靠的指标。

examination_example.sentence: It was not popularized until years <highlight>later</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它直到多年后才普及。

examination_example.sentence: 49 years <highlight>later</highlight>, Apollo 11 reached the moon, and the famed newspaper published an apology to Goddard.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 49年后，阿波罗11号到达月球，这家著名的报纸发表了对Goddard的道歉。

sense_info_list.en: belonging or taking place near the end of a particular time or period
sense_info_list.zh: 近末期的; 临结尾的

examination_example.sentence: In Estonia and Ireland, for example, the number of death has fallen by about two thirds since the <highlight>late</highlight> 1990s.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 例如，自20世纪90年代末以来，爱沙尼亚和爱尔兰的死亡人数下降了约三分之二。

examination_example.sentence: In his <highlight>later</highlight> years, Marconi exerted a tremendous influence on all aspects of people's life.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 马可尼晚年对人们生活的方方面面都产生了巨大的影响。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Late</highlight> in 2019, it was announced that US actor James Dean, who died in 1955, will star in a Vietnam War film.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 2019年末，有消息称，1955年去世的美国演员詹姆斯·迪恩将出演一部越南战争电影。

sense_info_list.en: up to the immediate present; most recent or most up-to-date

examination_example.sentence: Her <highlight>latest</highlight> documentary.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 她最新的纪录片。

examination_example.sentence: Recently, Jane, you've become quite a celebrity since the release of your <highlight>latest</highlight> documentary.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Jane，自从你最新的纪录片发布以来，最近你已经成为一个名人了。

examination_example.sentence: In 1924 he convinced the British government to encircle the world with a chain of wireless stations using the <highlight>latest</highlight> technology.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 1924年，他说服英国政府用最新的技术建立无线电台，环绕世界。

sense_info_list.en: doing something or taking place after the expected, proper, or usual time

examination_example.sentence: Let me just call my mom and let her know I'll be home a little bit <highlight>later</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 让我给我妈打个电话告诉她我晚点回来。

examination_example.sentence: Late in 2019, it was announced that US actor James Dean will star in a Vietnam War film scheduled for release <highlight>later</highlight> this year.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 2019年末，有消息称，美国演员詹姆斯·迪恩将出演一部越南战争电影，该片定于今年晚些时候上映。

sense_info_list.en: at a time following an earlier time

examination_example.sentence: We don't have the strength of chimpanzees (大猩猩) because we've given up animal strength to manipulate subtle instruments, like hammers, spears, and—<highlight>later</highlight>—pens and pencils.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们没有大猩猩的力量，因为我们已经放弃了动物的力量来操纵微妙的工具，如锤子、长矛，以及后来的笔和铅笔。

examination_example.sentence: A trick <highlight>later</highlight> repeated in the recent Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker, which was filmed after Fisher's death in 2016.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这一伎俩后来在最近的《星球大战：天行者的崛起》中重演，该片是在2016年费雪去世后拍摄的。

word_usage.usage: late的最高级latest的意思是“最新的”“最近的”，而不是“最后的”，表示最后的一般用last。

用数字表示“年代”时，年代前的定冠词the不可省略，如：
误 It happened in late 1960s.
正 It happened in the late 1960s.
“(做某事)迟到”须用be late for; “(到某地)迟到”须用be late at。

late的形容词形式和副词形式相同。注意lately（“最近，近来”）并不是late的副词形式。
汤姆上学迟到了，第一节课没赶上。
误 Tom came to school lately and missed the first lesson.
正 Tom came to school late and missed the first lesson.

examination_example.sentence: It is never too <highlight>late</highlight> to change your job.

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: adj. 后半部分的；后者；第二个；最近的；最后阶段的

word_family.mean: adj. 晚的；迟的；迟来的；已故的；最近的；最新的；后期；以前的；原来的；晚期的

examination_example.sentence: A moment <highlight>later</highlight>, Wasp flew around Zebra's head.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 过了一会儿，黄蜂绕着斑马的头飞来飞去。

examination_example.sentence: "She wasn't making sounds," <highlight>later</highlight> the firefighter said of the girl, whose exact age he didn't know.
examination_example.sentence_trans: “她没有发出声音”，后来消防队员谈到这个他不知道确切年龄的女孩时说。

examination_example.sentence: A few minutes <highlight>later</highlight>, he drove up in a car, and put the suitcases inside.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 几分钟后，他开车过来，把手提箱放了进去。

sense_info_list.en: doing something or taking place after the expected, proper, or usual time

examination_example.sentence: If you stay out too <highlight>late</highlight>, your parents will worry about you.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果你在外面呆得太晚，你父母会担心你的。

examination_example.sentence: He hardly stays up <highlight>late</highlight>, and he is an early bird.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他几乎不熬夜，并且起床很早。

examination_example.sentence: It is raining heavily, but none of the students are <highlight>late</highlight> for school.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 雨下得很大，但没有一个学生上学迟到。

sense_info_list.en: up to the immediate present; most recent or most up-to-date

examination_example.sentence: I'd like to share with you the <highlight>latest</highlight> news about the height of Qomolangma.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我想和你们一起分享关于珠穆朗玛峰高度的最新消息。

examination_example.sentence: Because electronic maps are easier to use and can show the <highlight>latest</highlight> road situation.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 因为电子地图更好用，可以显示最新的路况。

examination_example.sentence: Scientists are recommending the <highlight>latest</highlight> talking robots.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 科学家们正在推荐最新的会说话的机器人。

sense_info_list.en: belonging or taking place near the end of a particular time or period
sense_info_list.zh: 近末期的; 临结尾的

examination_example.sentence: It's <highlight>late</highlight> autumn now.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 现在是深秋。

examination_example.sentence: One cup of coffee in the <highlight>late</highlight> afternoon caused him to stay awake almost all night.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 下午晚些时候喝了一杯咖啡，导致他几乎彻夜未眠。

examination_example.sentence: I like to go to a swimming pool in the <highlight>late</highlight> afternoon after studying hard at school all day.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在学校努力学习了一整天之后，我喜欢在下午晚些时候去游泳池。

word_usage.usage: late的最高级latest的意思是“最新的”“最近的”，而不是“最后的”，表示最后的一般用last。

用数字表示“年代”时，年代前的定冠词the不可省略，如：
误 It happened in late 1960s.
正 It happened in the late 1960s.
“(做某事)迟到”须用be late for; “(到某地)迟到”须用be late at。

late的形容词形式和副词形式相同。注意lately（“最近，近来”）并不是late的副词形式。
汤姆上学迟到了，第一节课没赶上。
误 Tom came to school lately and missed the first lesson.
正 Tom came to school late and missed the first lesson.
